Feature: Customer Support and User Feedback
   In order to enhance customer satisfaction and engagement
   As a user
   I want accessible support and the ability to leave product feedback

Scenario: Easy-to-Access Help Section
   Given the user requires assistance
   When the user navigates to the Help section
   Then the section should include FAQs, a search function, and contact options for customer service

Scenario: Contributing Product Reviews
   Given the user has purchased a product
   When the user submits a star rating and text feedback for the product
   Then the review should be displayed under the product for other users to see